          <l>maṟattaliṉūṅ killaiyāṅ kēṭu</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
          <l>There is no greater boon than dharma; than forgetting it</l>
          <l>no greater ruin exists.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
